name: Gree-Z
description: If you’re stuck in a rut and your gears are grindin’ maybe your game needs some double timin! Get back on track and flow like a mac with your friend that’s always got your back. Remember, always keep it Gree-Z!  It’s another collectable trading card in the Los Demonios Amigos series. New cards drop every Tuesday.  Collect ‘em, trade ’em, get ‘em all! Keep an eye on Twitter for rare 1 of 1 color variants and remixes dropping randomly! Check me on IG and Twitter @losdemoniosamigos and @marksarmel. Website at marksarmel.com
